href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104viv1665702797646.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/viv1665702797646.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/viv1665702797646.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"viv1665702797646\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                          \n Menu Library\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use this editor to define menu bars, drop-down menus, and popup menus for use in desktop applications.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"viv1665702797646__section_w77ab1b7b1_w78ab1b7_w79ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"viv1665702797646__section_rx2_l1g_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1239243e60\">Properties</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"viv1665702797646__ul_u43_l1g_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"viv1665702797646__li_d3425e1_d3426e1_d3427e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nyk1665702811182.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nyk1665702811182.html\" title=\"The structure of the current menu object, for example a menu bar and its associated dropdown menus.\">Menu Path</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"viv1665702797646__li_d3428e1_d3429e1_d3430e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zwi1665702662755.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zwi1665702662755.html\" title=\"Label of a menu item (including optional icon), as displayed in the menu bar or menu. To include an icon, use a GOLD ! between the image and text values.\">Item</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"viv1665702797646__li_d3431e1_d3432e1_d3433e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bhj1665702662245.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bhj1665702662245.html\" title=\"Name of the menu to display from this item.\">Referenced Menu</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"viv1665702797646__li_d3434e1_d3435e1_d3436e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Menu</span>\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"viv1665702797646__li_d3437e1_d3438e1_d3439e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ffa1665702662616.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ffa1665702662616.html\" title=\"Type of menu item.\">Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"viv1665702797646__li_d3440e1_d3441e1_d3442e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Item</span>\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"viv1665702797646__li_d3443e1_d3444e1_d3445e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rem1665702662320.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rem1665702662320.html\" title=\"Name to represent the keyboard shortcut for accessing this menu item.\">Accelerator</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"viv1665702797646__li_d3446e1_d3447e1_d3448e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uve1665702662391.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uve1665702662391.html\" title=\"Determines whether the menu or menu item is automatically enables when the menu is first displayed. Any ProcScript code referenced in the Predisplay trigger overrides this property.\">Enable Item by Default</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"viv1665702797646__li_d3449e1_d3450e1_d3451e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"chj1665702662461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/chj1665702662461.html\" title=\"Text displayed in the message area at run time when the cursor is moved onto the menu object.\">Hint Text</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"viv1665702797646__section_kj4_m1g_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1239243e160\">How to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"viv1665702797646__ul_k5r_m1g_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"viv1665702797646__li_d3452e1_d3453e1_d3454e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nvc1705580311070.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nvc1705580311070.html\" title=\"You can define menu bars, context menus, drop-down menus, and dynamic menus for the application as a whole or for individual form components. Menus are defined and deployed in libraries.\">Define and Use Menus</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"viv1665702797646__li_d3455e1_d3456e1_d3457e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nme1665702662077.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nme1665702662077.html\" title=\"You can dynamically control the content of a drop-down or pop-up menus using ProcScript. First define a menu containing a menu item of type Dynamic Menu, then build the dynamic menu in the preDisplay trigger, and handle the use selection of an item in the option trigger.\">Define Dynamic Menus</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/crm1665702872883.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Menu Objects</a><p>Uniface enables you to define menu bar, drop-down menu, and pop-up menu objects for use in Windows applications.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bxw1705577952463.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Menu Items</a><p>A menu item can be a menu option that results in an action, a reference to another menu, such as a cascaded menu or included menu, or a separator for grouping items. Menu items have associated triggers in which to program the conditions under which they are displayed and the action they perform.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533039\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533039\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Menu Library Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Menu Library Use this editor to define menu bars, drop-down menus, and popup menus for use in desktop applications. Properties Menu Path Item Referenced Menu Menu Description Type Item Description Accelerator Enable Item by Default Hint Text How to Define and Use Menus Define Dynamic Menus Related Links Menu Objects Uniface enables you to define menu bar, drop-down menu, and pop-up menu objects for use in Windows applications. Menu Items A menu item can be a menu option that results in an action, a reference to another menu, such as a cascaded menu or included menu, or a separator for grouping items. Menu items have associated triggers in which to program the conditions under which they are displayed and the action they perform. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}